---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-navy py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 border-t border-white/5">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Compliance block -->
    <div class="text-white/40 text-xs leading-relaxed space-y-3">
      <p>
        <strong class="text-white/70">DSCRBroker.com is a lead matching service.</strong> We are not a lender, bank, or licensed mortgage broker. Licensed broker activity, including pre-qualification, pre-approval, file structuring, lender selection, rate quotes, credit pulls, and income verification, is performed by your matched specialist. For Florida deals, your matched specialist is John Peisner / Barrett Financial Group, NMLS #239185.
      </p>
      <p>
        Equal Housing Opportunity. All loan products are offered by independent licensed mortgage brokers and lenders. This is not a commitment to lend. Loan terms, eligibility, and approval are subject to the matched specialist's underwriting review and the originating lender's program requirements. Property types, locations, and borrower scenarios may not qualify under all programs.
      </p>
      <p>
        By submitting your information, you consent to be contacted by your matched DSCR specialist via phone, SMS, or email regarding your inquiry, even if your number is on a Do Not Call list. Consent is not a condition of any loan or service. Message and data rates may apply.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Links + EHO -->
    <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between gap-4">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-xs text-white/30">
        <a href="/privacy-policy/" class="hover:text-white/60 transition-colors">Privacy Policy</a>
        <span>|</span>
        <a href="/terms-of-service/" class="hover:text-white/60 transition-colors">Terms of Service</a>
        <span>|</span>
        <span>© {currentYear} DSCRBroker.com</span>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <span class="text-xs text-white/40 font-medium">Equal Housing Opportunity</span>
        <svg class="h-7 w-7 text-white/40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 12l9-9 9 9M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h12a1 1 0 001-1V10" />
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 21V13h6v8" />
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
